    "title": "SeaKing H10 Black Fiberglass Fillet Table (L32.7\" x W15.7\")",
    "body_html": "<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Sea King SK-H10</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Colour: Black</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Meet the SeaKing SK-H10, a premium addition to the SeaKing lineup. Crafted with high-quality </span><span>composite materials, this cutting board features a UV-resistant PE plastic surface. Designed for </span><span>efficiency, it includes a generously sized sink with a drain fitting and hose. The </span><span>rear boasts a spacious knife tray, maximising cutting space while minimising onboard footprint.</span></p>",
